#Text=PETA , animal rights groups and the Animal Liberation Front
#Text=DS : How do you feel when you hear other animal rights organizations coming out against PETA ?
#Text=IN : Oh , I do n’t mind .
#Text=I think somebody has to push the envelope .
#Text=If you say something someone already agrees with , then what ’s the point ?
#Text=So we make some more conservative animal protection organizations uncomfortable .
#Text=They do n’t want to be associated with us because it will be embarrassing for them .
#Text=I understand that .
#Text=Our own members write to us sometimes and say ,
#Text=“ Oh , why did you do this ? I do n’t want anybody to know I ’m a PETA member . ”
#Text=For some of us we agree cordially , like that Humane Society man .

#Text=We exchange e-mails all the time and I nag him that he needs to take a stronger position on some things and stop mealy-mouthing , and he nags me in his e-mails that it ’s about time I condemn such-and-such .
#Text=“ It does n’t do any good for you to stick up for such-and-such . ”
#Text=DS : What is something you have been asked to condemn ?
#Text=IN : He wants us to condemn illegal acts .
#Text=DS : By the Animal Liberation Front ?
#Text=IN : Yes , those getting the animals out of the laboratories , and I wo n’t do it because if it was my animal I would be happy .
#Text=If it was Little Man [ David Shankbone ’ s dog , pictured in the lead photo ] I would be happy .
#Text=DS : So you are okay with ALF activities ?
#Text=Some of that was covered in the film .
#Text=IN : It was only marginally covered .
#Text=There was only so much you could focus on and in such a way .
#Text=There were n’t rebuttals to many things , which was disturbing .

#Text=Like when that woman said PETA is not doing any good , I would love to have seen the whole list of endless victories we have had , starting with General Motors switching to mannequins in crash tests —
#Text=DS : L’Oreal , Maybelline —
#Text=IN : All of it .
#Text=There ’s a huge huge list of everything .
#Text=DS : How do you feel about the ALF ?
#Text=IN : I wrote a book called Free the Animals , and it ’s about the Animal Liberation Front since its inception in the United States .
#Text=Not about the ALF overseas , where it began , but its inception here going to about 199-something .
#Text=I talked about how I do support getting animals out in the same way I would have supported getting human slaves out , child labor , sex slaves , the whole lot .
#Text=But I do n’t support burning .
#Text=I do n’t support arson .
#Text=I would rather that these buildings were n’t standing , so on some level I understand .
#Text=I just do n’t like the idea of that .
#Text=Maybe that is wishy-washy of me , because I do n’t want those buildings standing if they are going to hurt anyone .
#Text=And the ALF has never hurt mice nor man .
